Package drjoliv.jbullet

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Graph
    A Graph containing information within the jBullet database.
    Node
    A Node within the jBullet graph database.
    NodeBuilder
    NodeBuilder presents a fluent API for building Nodes.
    PlatformServices
    Provides services to Plugins.
    Relationship
    A RelationShip between two nodes within
    RelationshipBuilder
    Builds relationships between nodes.

    Attribute.ListStringAttribute

    Attribute.LongAttribute
